readme:
# `postcss-sort-media` sort @media > Copy from [`css-mqpacker`](https://www.npmjs.com/package/css-mqpacker) and [`sort-css-media-queries`](https://www.npmjs.com/package/sort-css-media-queries) because of the package `css-mqpacker` has been deprecated.

[![NPM version](https://img.shields.io/npm/v/postcss-sort-media.svg)](https://www.npmjs.com/package/postcss-sort-media) [![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-brightgreen.svg)](https://github.com/gotoeasy/npm-packages/blob/master/LICENSE)

## Sample ``` let sortmedia = require('postcss-sort-media')({desktopFirst: false}); require('postcss')([sortmedia]).process(css); ```
